                    PUBLIC COMMENT ON STATE PLAN

                       POLICIES AND PROCEDURES

   The State Plan is being made available for public review. Please
   note that the reports available on this page are in Rich Text
   Format (RTF) and should open with any word processing software.  If
   you need a hard copy version of the report, please contact Eva
   Collier at the address and phone number, or email listed below.
   Comments will be accepted on the plan until February 16, 2001.
   Comments can be submitted via fax or electronic mail at:
   Attention: Eva Collier (FAX) (916) 263-7472
   evacollier@dor.ca.gov
   Comments can be made in writing and mailed to:
   Eva Collier, Research Analyst
   Research, Evaluation, Planning, and Statistics Section
   2000 Evergreen Street
   Sacramento, CA 95815-3896
   Given the limited time available for preparation of the plan and
   since there are no significant program changes in the plan, an
   extensive mailing would not be practical nor necessary for this
   plan.
